<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
<h4 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Snel inzicht en overzicht in overheidsuitgaven</span></h4>
<div class="et_pb_blurb_description"><p>Zoek en filter Financile Instrumenten, Apparaatsuitgaven, Inkoopuitgaven, Provinciale en Gemeentelijke subsidies in seconden voor snel inzicht.</p></div>

<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
<h4 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Zoek en filter op ontvangers, regelingen en artikelen</span></h4>
<div class="et_pb_blurb_description"><p>Duik de diepte in en signaleer eenvoudig opvallende uitgaven en heldere patronen.</p></div>

</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_3 et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_blurb_position_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
<div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
<div class="et_pb_main_blurb_image"><span class="et_pb_image_wrap et_pb_only_image_mode_wrap"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="800" src="https://rijksuitgaven.nl/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Snelinzicht_wit.webp" alt="" srcset="https://rijksuitgaven.nl/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Snelinzicht_wit.webp 800w, https://rijksuitgaven.nl/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Snelinzicht_wit-480x480.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 800px, 100vw" class="et-waypoint et_pb_animation_off et_pb_animation_off_tablet et_pb_animation_off_phone wp-image-9448" /></span></div>

<div class="et_pb_with_border et_pb_module dsm_text_notation dsm_text_notation_0 et_pb_bg_layout_light">
<div class="et_pb_module_inner">
<h1 class="dsm-text-notation-main et_pb_module_header"><span data-notation="[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;underline&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;#0e3261&quot;,&quot;stroke-width&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;iterations&quot;:&quot;3&quot;,&quot;brackets&quot;:&quot;left|right&quot;,&quot;viewport&quot;:&quot;80%&quot;,&quot;delay&quot;:&quot;0ms&quot;,&quot;divi-animate&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;divi-animate-duration&quot;:&quot;1000ms&quot;,&quot;divi-animate-delay&quot;:&quot;0ms&quot;}]" class="dsm-text-notation-middle">Probeer nu: </span><span class="dsm-text-notation-after">doorzoek uitgaven 2024</span></h1>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">jQuery(function($) {
const TABLE_IDS = ['table_1', 'table_2'];
const NS = '.descfirst';
function enableDescFirst(api) {
const $container = $(api.table().container());
$container.off('click' + NS, 'thead th');
$container.on('click' + NS, 'thead th', function(e) {
const $th = $(this);
if (!$th.hasClass('sorting') &&
!$th.hasClass('sorting_asc') &&
!$th.hasClass('sorting_desc')) {
return;
}
e.preventDefault();
e.stopImmediatePropagation();
const colIndex = api.column(this).index();
const current = api.order();
if (!current.length || current[0][0] !== colIndex) {
api.order([colIndex, 'desc']).draw();
} else {
const dir = current[0][1] === 'desc' ? 'asc' : 'desc';
api.order([colIndex, dir]).draw();
}
});
}
function handleTableEvent(settings) {
const id = settings.sTableId;
if (TABLE_IDS.includes(id)) {
const api = new $.fn.dataTable.Api(settings);
enableDescFirst(api);
}
}
$(document).on('init.dt', function(e, settings) {
handleTableEvent(settings);
});
TABLE_IDS.forEach(function(id) {
const sel = '#' + id;
if ($.fn.dataTable.isDataTable(sel)) {
enableDescFirst($(sel).DataTable());
}
});
$(document).on('draw.dt', function(e, settings) {
handleTableEvent(settings);
});
});</script><style>

<script type="text/javascript">jQuery(function($) {
const TABLE_IDS = ['table_1', 'table_2'];
const NS = '.descfirst';
function enableDescFirst(api) {
const $container = $(api.table().container());
$container.off('click' + NS, 'thead th');
$container.on('click' + NS, 'thead th', function(e) {
const $th = $(this);
if (!$th.hasClass('sorting') &&
!$th.hasClass('sorting_asc') &&
!$th.hasClass('sorting_desc')) {
return;
}
e.preventDefault();
e.stopImmediatePropagation();
const colIndex = api.column(this).index();
const current = api.order();
if (!current.length || current[0][0] !== colIndex) {
api.order([colIndex, 'desc']).draw();
} else {
const dir = current[0][1] === 'desc' ? 'asc' : 'desc';
api.order([colIndex, dir]).draw();
}
});
}
function handleTableEvent(settings) {
const id = settings.sTableId;
if (TABLE_IDS.includes(id)) {
const api = new $.fn.dataTable.Api(settings);
enableDescFirst(api);
}
}
$(document).on('init.dt', function(e, settings) {
handleTableEvent(settings);
});
TABLE_IDS.forEach(function(id) {
const sel = '#' + id;
if ($.fn.dataTable.isDataTable(sel)) {
enableDescFirst($(sel).DataTable());
}
});
$(document).on('draw.dt', function(e, settings) {
handleTableEvent(settings);
});
});</script><style>

<div class="et_pb_code_inner"><style>
/* Ensure all carousels have the same height */
.dsm_image_carousel_container {
height: 350px; /* Adjust as needed */
}

.dsm_image_carousel_item img {
transition: transform 1.5s ease;
}

.dsm_image_carousel_item:hover img {
transform: scale(3);
}
</style></div>
</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_code et_pb_code_2">
<div class="et_pb_code_inner"><script>
document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
document.querySelectorAll(".dsm_image_carousel_item img").forEach((img) => {
img.addEventListener("mousemove", function (e) {
let imgRect = this.getBoundingClientRect();
let offsetX = e.clientX - imgRect.left;
let offsetY = e.clientY - imgRect.top;
let percentX = (offsetX / imgRect.width) * 100;
let percentY = (offsetY / imgRect.height) * 100;

this.style.transformOrigin = `${percentX}% ${percentY}%`;
});
});
});
</script></div>
